
1. Inet Raw sockets
	- bound to IP layer

  Application areas
	- Apps intending to use application space 3rd party transport protocols
	- Apps intending to use lighter versions of TCP/UDP(lwip)
	- Network Diagnostic tools like traceroute, ping,.....
	- Network sniffers
		- traffic monitors
		- protocol analysers
		- port scanners
		- packet analysys tools
		- eg: tcpdump, ethreal, airsnort,...

2. packet rawsockets
	- bound to DLL layer

   Application  areas
	- Apps designed to use usermode TCP/IP libraries
	- Apps desgined to use custom/proprietory protocol implementations
	- Network Diagnostic tools
	- Network sniffers




	
	
	
